Richard Windsor, global technology 
analyst at Nomura International Plc, talks about the outlook 
for the technology industry in 2012 and recommendation of 
Microsoft Corp., SAP AG and Samsung Electronics Co.   He speaks from Dubai with  Mark Barton  on Bloomberg 
Television's "The Pulse." (Source: Bloomberg)  Running Time: 04:07
 